	Clairvoyance: clairvoyance buff
	Regeneration: regeneration buff
	Swiftness: swiftness buff
	Ironskin: ironskin buff
	Wrath: wrath buff
	Rage: rage buff
	Lifeforce: life force buff
	Endurance: Endurance buff
	FishingPotion: fishing potion buff
	Sonar: sonar buff
	Crate: crate buff
	WaterWalking: water walking buff
	Calm: calm buff
	Inferno: inferno buff
	Shine: shine buff
	Spelunker: spelunker buff
	Hunter: hunter buff
	WeaponImbueFire: Weapon Imbue: Fire
