	WeaponImbuePartyDesc: melee attacks cause confetti to appear
	WeaponImbueNanites: Weapon Imbue: Nanites
	WeaponImbueNanitesDesc: melee attacks inflict nanites debuff
	MinionImbueFireDesc: your minions inflict on fire
	MinionImbuePoisonDesc: your minions inflict poison
	MinionImbueShadowDesc: your minions inflict shadowflame
	MinionImbueVenomDesc: your minions inflict acid venom
	MagicWeaponImbueFire: Weapon Imbue: Fire
	MagicWeaponImbueFireDesc: magic attacks inflict on fire debuff
	MagicWeaponImbuePoison: Weapon Imbue: Poison
	MagicWeaponImbuePoisonDesc: magic attacks inflict poison debuff
